Flask app is run on the gunicorn production server on port 8000
- http://127.0.0.1:8000

The service file is located at /etc/systemd/system/4910project.service
Check status with systemctl status 4910project.service
OR restart with systemctl restart 4910project.service

Using nginx as our proxy. Configs in /etc/nginx

Using a user python without a venv as the enviroment with pyenv